Package: ggiplot
Title: ggplot2 Equivalents of fixest::iplot()
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Grant",
           family = "McDermott",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "grantmcd@uoregon.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7883-8573"))
Description: Provides ggplot2 equivalents of fixest::iplot(). Enables some
	additional functionality and convenience features, including grouped 
	mutli_fixest object facetting and programatic updating of existing plots
	(e.g. themes and aesthetics).
